    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MAW是一部叙事驱动的冒险游戏，讲述了在压抑的社会中，一名酷儿侦探苦苦挣扎于自我的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/ee4ed04029327727d8f3b8d97f6331c8.poster.avif?t=1767549461\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/ee4ed04029327727d8f3b8d97f6331c8.webm?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/ee4ed04029327727d8f3b8d97f6331c8.mp4?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面你内心的野性！嗅寻线索，舔尽一切来获取信息。是压抑天性还是接受真我坦荡迎接世界的敌意！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/5d701a52369c5c8941d0c5c45d640aa1.poster.avif?t=1767549461\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/5d701a52369c5c8941d0c5c45d640aa1.webm?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/5d701a52369c5c8941d0c5c45d640aa1.mp4?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查犯罪事件。隐藏你的身份，一旦暴露，你的结局将是...甚至更糟，如果你妈妈愿意的话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/bf48258692e4322046a0b9ba1163d74f.poster.avif?t=1767549461\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/bf48258692e4322046a0b9ba1163d74f.webm?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/bf48258692e4322046a0b9ba1163d74f.mp4?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立长久的关系。与其他动物交谈、调情或是观察、审问他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏角色将会记住你作出的选择。你的行为、样貌和性格也会导向不同的故事线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/c8e3c1fc93f8865f2d2ff316e753bb4e.poster.avif?t=1767549461\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/c8e3c1fc93f8865f2d2ff316e753bb4e.webm?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/c8e3c1fc93f8865f2d2ff316e753bb4e.mp4?t=1767549461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MAW的故事部分基于个人经历，角色和事件均为虚构，但游戏所描绘的情感和无尽的挣扎都是真情实感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273860/extras/d4fa9c0ba70680f29270e6645ad9f2c5.avif?t=1767549461\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态叙事-角色会根据你的选择、性格、样貌而做出不同回应</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猛兽天性-使用动物本能（嗅、舔、听、察）来寻找线索，探索场景或与其他角色互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义外观-穿上不同服饰，看他人又如何待你</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可与多名角色建立关系</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的福瑞艺术收藏卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像狗狗一样奔跑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于作者真实经历改编的酷儿故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全人工制作，不使用任何生成式AI</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
